WelcomeResponseCallback - Class in me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.delivery.callback
AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the WELCOME SMTPResponse which is triggered after the connection is established to the SMTP Server It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
